Older women in an aging world: achieving health across the life course.

Bonita R(1), Howe AL.

Author information:
(1)Department of Medicine, University of Auckland, New Zealand.

This article, based on a report (Women, aging and health: achieving health 
across the life span) prepared for the WHO Global Commission on Women's Health 
under the guidance of WHO's Aging and Health Programme, presents demographic 
data that clearly demonstrate the need for recognition of the health of aging 
